<!-- Type Lattice -->
	<section xml:id="ref.types.lattice">
		<title>The Type Lattice</title>
		<section xml:id="ref.types.lattice.body">
			<para>
			Types in Orc form a bounded lattice. The lattice is ordered by the subtyping relation,
			its maximal element is <code>Top</code>, and its minimal element is <code>Bot</code>.
			Any two types have a join (least supertype) and a meet (greatest subtype). Often, the
			join is simply <code>Top</code> and the meet is simply <code>Bot</code>.			
			</para>
		</section>
		
